Man Wakes Up After Fatal Crash | Suburbanite | Full Thriller Movie

Late one night on his way home from work John falls asleep at the wheel and hits a man. He takes the body home, fully intending to cover it up when suddenly the unthinkable occurs, the man wakes up. Now John must decide how far he is willing to go to protect his family and his secret.

2013. Stars: Joe Nemmers, Jodie Moore, Frank Mosley
